OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss 'rules out' more     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdirect energy bill help for
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fall                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liz Truss has "ruled out" further      
OL,6, direct support for everyone to help    
OL,7, cover the cost of surging energy bills,
OL,8, sources close to her have told the BBC.
OL,10,FRishi Sunak, who is vying with her to  
OL,11,Fbecome the next prime minister, has    
OL,12,Fsaid the government "must provide some 
OL,13,Fdirect support to everyone".           
OL,15,FBut Ms Truss's team said she was not   
OL,16,Fconsidering further universal support, 
OL,17,Flike the #400 payment that all         
OL,18,Fhouseholds will receive this winter.   
OL,20,FReports suggest a VAT cut is an option.
